metadata.name: Hangry #1/100
metadata.description:
Hangry

Denise Rudolf Frank, *1993 in Vienna, studied painting at Central St. Martin’s, London and the Academy of Fine Arts in Vienna. Her expressions are a passionated plea for interpreted joie de vivre and concentrated zest for action.
